# Mark Security Services

A modern, secure, and professional website for **MarkMellon Security Services** — a leading private security company in Uganda.

> **Your Safety, Our Priority**

## ✨ Features

### Public Website
- Fully responsive dark-themed design (Black, Navy Blue & Gold accents)
- Glassmorphism effects and smooth animations
- Full-screen hero section with security imagery
- Services showcase with modal details
- Dynamic Projects / Clients gallery
- Careers page with job application form
- Contact form with Google Maps embed
- Mobile-optimized navigation with slide-in menu
- 404, 500, 403 & Maintenance error pages

### Admin Panel
- Secure login with Firebase Authentication
- Real-time Dashboard with key statistics
- Full CRUD operations for:
  - Services
  - Projects
  - Job Listings
- View and manage Contact Messages
- View Job Applications (with CV download support)
- Real-time notifications for new messages & applications
- Responsive sidebar navigation

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML5, Tailwind CSS, Vanilla JavaScript
- **Backend/Database**: Firebase Realtime Database
- **Authentication**: Firebase Authentication
- **File Storage**: Firebase Storage (for logos, images, CVs)
- **Icons**: Font Awesome 6
- **Animations**: CSS + Tailwind transitions

